### bghoul <model>
Load a ghoul model as background to bolt other areas to.

### backdrop
Set background image/colour.
- `tile` — tile image
- `stretch` — stretch image
- `center` — center image
- `left` — flush left
- `right` — flush right
- `bgcolor <colour>` — background fill colour

